Reno Omokri has tackled supporters of the former Governor of Anambra state, Peter Obi, who who are saying that Peter Obi’s resignation from the People’s Democratic Party will lead to the end of the party. Reno Omokri gave instances where the party won several elections when Peter Obi was not in the party
Reno Omokri said that you are saying that Peter Obi’s exit is the end of the People’s Democratic Party, but he was not in the party in 1999, 2003, 2007 and 2011 when the PDP won the Presidential elections. It was only in 2015 and 2019 that he joined the party the the PDP lost




